formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
1. The estimated costs mentioned in Column A is as provided by the management. The estimates should not be construed as certification of forecasts or estimates. The preparation of the accompanying Statement is the responsibility of the Management. This responsibility includes designing, implementing and maintaining internal control relevant to the preparation and presentation of the Statement, and applying an appropriate basis of preparation; and making estimates that are reasonable in the circumstances. 
2. The details mentioned in Annexure A such as carpet area, booking status, unit consideration, date of agreement to sale, encumbrance status, name, KYC and mobile numbers of allottees are as provided by the management. Received amount has been verified with the books of accounts.
3. Lease deed has been executed for entire fifth floor for a period of 9 years. However, since the nature of transaction is of lease/rent and not to transfer the title of the units, intention is not that of sale. Considering the same, these inventories are considered as unbooked inventory.
4. Finance has also been procured from Shriram City Union Finance Ltd, however the loan is secured by providing collateral other than project land. Interest for Shriram City Union Finance Ltd is not considered as part of interest cost for the purpose of this certificate.
5.The certificate is addressed to and provided to the promoters of the project solely for the purpose to enable comply with requirement of RERA , and should not be used by any other person or for any other purpose. Accordingly, we do not accept or assume any liability or any duty of care for any other purpose or to any other person to whom this certificate is shown or into whose hands it may come without our prior consent in writing.
6. Unit 408 allotted to Yogesh Hingorani has been cancelled however refund is pending to be issued
